{"tid":2390381,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一個人係學校食飯比人恥笑","createTime":"2021-02-01T13:34:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T14:04:31.000Z","uid":313692,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"30ed1bb92f2518f14ff01fce84d8c027f5155470","tid":2390381,"uid":313692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T13:34:35.000Z","msg":"今日返學校溫書<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗住食埋飯先走<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見自己一個咪買頹飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果食緊個陣成日見到成班人聯群結黨望住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n感覺佢哋好似成班笑緊我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問佢哋「望乜撚嘢啊」<br />\n但見佢哋成班都大大隻咁最後又唔敢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家哭𠹌咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解一個人食飯都要比人恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e287dffa279a41f20528a4eeecd7d333d1392840","tid":2390381,"uid":308375,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T13:35:25.000Z","msg":"平時拎盒飯入廁所食冇人笑到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b13ee5cdc2085e0a841021afe8ecafcbe7a30c5","tid":2390381,"uid":385667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score